%bigsql

-- Transaction raw BUSINESS DATA 

SELECT
	TX.CREATION_TIME,
	VARCHAR(TX.ARG_0, 24) AS TX_TYPE,
	VARCHAR(TX.ARG_1, 512) AS TX_PAYLOAD
FROM
	ALL_TX AS TX FETCH FIRST 10 ROWS ONLY;

paragraphs.text:
%bigsql

-- Accessing individual BUSINESS DATA items

SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER() AS CLAIM_SEQUENCE,
	JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'username', 's:64' ) AS OWNER,
    TX.CREATION_TIME AS CLAIM_REGISTERED,
	JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'description', 's:64' ) AS CLAIM_DESCRIPTION,
	JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'is_theft', 's:10' ) AS IS_THEFT
FROM
    ALL_TX AS TX
WHERE
    TX.ARG_0 = 'claim_file';

-- Number of insured items and avg exposure per contract type

SELECT
    JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'contract_type_uuid', 's:36') AS CONTRACT_TYPE,
    CAST( SUM(JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'item.price', 'f')) / COUNT(TX.ARG_1) AS DECIMAL(8,2)) AS AVG_EXPOSURE
FROM
   ALL_TX AS TX
WHERE
    TX.ARG_0 = 'contract_create'
GROUP BY
    JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'contract_type_uuid', 's:36');

--
-- Combined 
---

WITH 
    CONTRACTS AS (
        SELECT
            JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'contract_type_uuid', 's:36') AS CONTRACT_TYPE_UUID,
            JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'uuid', 's:36') AS CONTRACT_UUID,
            JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'item.price', 's:10') AS CONTRACT_AMOUNT
        FROM
            ALL_TX AS TX
        WHERE
            TX.ARG_0 = 'contract_create'), 
    CLAIMS AS (
        SELECT
            JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'contract_uuid', 's:36') AS CONTRACT_UUID,
            JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'uuid', 's:36') AS CLAIM_UUID,
            JSON_VAL(SYSTOOLS.JSON2BSON(TX.ARG_1), 'reimbursable', 's:10') AS CLAIM_AMOUNT
        FROM
            ALL_TX AS TX
        WHERE
            TX.ARG_0 = 'claim_process')
SELECT 
    CONTRACTS.CONTRACT_TYPE_UUID,
    --CONTRACTS.CONTRACT_UUID,
    COUNT(CLAIMS.CONTRACT_UUID) AS CLAIM_COUNT,
    SUM(CONTRACTS.CONTRACT_AMOUNT) AS CONTRACT_SUM_AMOUNT,
    SUM(CLAIMS.CLAIM_AMOUNT) AS CLAIM_SUM_AMOUNT,
    SUM(CLAIMS.CLAIM_AMOUNT) / SUM(CONTRACTS.CONTRACT_AMOUNT) * 100 AS RATIO_PERCENT
FROM 
    CONTRACTS, 
    CLAIMS
WHERE
    CONTRACTS.CONTRACT_UUID = CLAIMS.CONTRACT_UUID
GROUP BY
    CONTRACTS.CONTRACT_TYPE_UUID;
